                Mr. Head
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-9ea01bd0-7438-4fed-81d5-9f37ce4de9f4" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
