    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">The hon. Gentleman himself has had it within his power to receive a written answer to this Question for some time, but it was by his own choice that he deferred the Question in order to get a verbal answer. I do not personally <span id="204" class="column-number" data-column-number="204"></span> think that the very considerable prominence given to this in the "Daily Worker" has the effect which the hon. Gentleman fears.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-b3f0de2a-9879-43fc-aae3-ab67d56dc7a8" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
